      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING O'REILLY (1) well back settling but did wind up strongly to finish 5th and beaten only 1.5 lengths (26.14) at this track. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Can bounce back. ELEVATE (6) missed the frame last time when fourth (28.69) at Bendigo but prior to that had two placings in a row. Has a strong winning record here. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings four times from seven attempts. Shapes as one to consider. MISS COCO (4) has been out of the placings at her last two outings but shapes well for this if she can recapture her dominant win a few runs back, getting around Geelong over 400m in 22.43. Should be in this for a long way. SAINT TAY (2) cannot be ruled out.",
